---
title: Bacon, Chicken Breast, Leek and Mushroom Pie with Mustard and Mashed Potato Top
description: This Bacon, Chicken Breast, Leek and Mushroom Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W37_UK_F14829-3_Main_add_swap_low-0457c6cf.jpg
